sequenceDiagram
    actor Eatme
    participant Test as supertest / CLI harness
    participant API as Express server
    participant Events as EventSystem
    participant VM as tweedle-vm
    participant Evidence as evidence dir

    Eatme->>Test: run e2e scenario
    Test->>API: GET /api/health
    API-->>Test: running
    Test->>API: POST /api/launch
    API-->>Test: launched

    loop add objects
        Test->>API: POST /api/scene/add-object
        API->>Evidence: scene-object-added.json
        API-->>Test: added
    end

    loop register handlers
        Test->>API: POST /api/events/register
        API->>Events: register(...)
        API->>Evidence: event-register.json
        API-->>Test: registrationId
    end

    Test->>API: POST /api/events/fire
    API->>Events: fire(...)
    Events-->>API: triggered handlers
    API->>Evidence: event-fire.json
    API-->>Test: triggered[]

    Test->>API: POST /api/world/run
    API->>VM: executeProject(...)
    VM-->>API: execution_log
    API->>Evidence: run-world-result.json
    API-->>Test: completed

    Test->>Evidence: verify accumulated JSON artifacts
